props.title: Experience the Luxury of Gold Tanning
props.content: At Ohana Sun Tanning, we offer an exclusive Gold Tanning service that elevates your tanning experience to new heights. Our state-of-the-art tanning beds utilize advanced technology to deliver a rich, bronze glow while nourishing your skin with essential vitamins and minerals. Each session is tailored to your skin type and desired results, ensuring a safe and effective tanning process. The soothing ambiance of our salon enhances your relaxation, making each visit feel like a mini-vacation. With our Gold Tanning service, you not only achieve a stunning tan but also enjoy the long-lasting benefits of beautifully hydrated skin. Embrace the sun-kissed look year-round with Ohana Sun Tanning, where your satisfaction and skin health are our top priorities.

props.title: Benefits of Gold

benefits.title: Premium Tanning Experience
benefits.description: Enjoy a luxurious tanning session that delivers a deep, golden glow while providing ultimate comfort and relaxation.

benefits.title: Enhanced Skin Care
benefits.description: Our Gold service includes advanced skin care technology to nourish and protect your skin during tanning, ensuring a healthier appearance.

benefits.title: Exclusive Member Discounts
benefits.description: As a Gold service member, you gain access to exclusive discounts on future tanning sessions and products, maximizing your value.

benefits.title: Personalized Tanning Plans
benefits.description: Receive tailored tanning plans designed by our experts to meet your individual skin type and tanning goals for optimal results.

props.description: Discover the many advantages of choosing Gold at Ohana Sun Tanning

props.title: What Clients Say About Gold
props.description: Hear from satisfied clients who've experienced our Gold.

testimonials.name: Christina Sierra
testimonials.review: This place, these people, the tan I have the luxury of wearing now, all beyond exceptional. I was pleasantly surprised by their honesty. One night, I'd gone in for a custom spray tan (Gail is a wildly talented custom sprayer!) and I lost my gold bracelet I'd been wearing for 13 years upon removing for tanning process. Once I realized it was gone, I called to see if perhaps someone had found it. To my pleasant surprise, the lovely Ariel had found it on the floor & said to come on in & get it. A less honest person could have kept it, as there is some value there, but mostly sentimental for me. It was returned safely to me when I arrived...& for this I shall always remain their loyal (& grateful!) customer. Thank you Ariel & Image Sun, you guys are the BEST!

faqs.answer: The Gold service includes a premium single tanning session, access to high-quality sunbeds, and complimentary tanning lotion for optimal results.
faqs.question: What is included in the Gold service for single tans?

faqs.answer: A typical Gold tanning session lasts about 20 minutes, ensuring you achieve a beautiful, even tan without overexposure.
faqs.question: How long does a typical Gold tanning session last?

faqs.answer: Yes, the Gold service can be tailored for sensitive skin. We recommend discussing your skin type with our staff for personalized advice.
faqs.question: Can I use the Gold service if I have sensitive skin?

faqs.answer: For best results, we recommend booking the Gold service 2-3 times a week, allowing your skin to recover between sessions.
faqs.question: How often can I book the Gold tanning service?

faqs.answer: We advise wearing comfortable, minimal clothing or swimwear to ensure an even tan. You may also bring your own tanning goggles for eye protection.
faqs.question: What should I wear during my Gold tanning session?

faqs.answer: Yes, clients must be at least 18 years old to use the Gold tanning service. Valid ID may be required at the time of booking.
faqs.question: Is there an age restriction for the Gold tanning service?
